  <scopecontent id="aspace_107124396a9965b4c32e0fe6dcdb6957">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>Collection contains research, correspondence, and teaching materials relating to the professional career of Bernd Lambert. A number of the materials focus on his work in Kiribati.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <bioghist id="aspace_8c593b62f44340126abea9a085c79fcf">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Bernd Lambert was a professor of anthropology emeritus and a faculty member in Cornell University's College of Arts and Sciences. His studies included kinship among the Pacific islanders of the Republic of Kiribas.</p>  </bioghist>
  <prefercite id="aspace_c03a44e39402db2f011dad8179a6475f">
    <head>Preferred Citation</head>
<p>Bernd Lambert papers, #14-25-4613. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
